    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="A Summer Night">
                <interpGrp type="theme">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="free">free</interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad">sad</interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="nature">nature</interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <p>I feel the breath of the summer night,</p>
                <p> Aromatic fire:</p>
                <p>The trees, the vines, the flowers are astir</p>
                <p> With tender desire.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>The white moths flutter about the lamp,</p>
                <p> Enamoured with light;</p>
                <p>And a thousand creates softly sing</p>
                <p> A song to the night!</p>
                <p/>
                <p>But I am alone, and how can I sing</p>
                <p> Praises to thee?</p>
                <p>Come, Night! unveil the beautiful soul</p>
                <p> That waiteth for me.</p>
            </div>
            
